snippet: Two veterinarians from Virginia who were reported missing while hiking in Glacier National Park were found alive Monday, family members and park officials said.
abstract: Veterinarians Jason Hiser and Neal Peckens from Virginia,  who were  reported missing while hiking in Glacier National Park in Montana, are found alive.
lead_paragraph: Two veterinarians from Virginia who were reported missing while hiking in Glacier National Park were found alive Monday, family members and park officials said.

headline.main: Montana: Two Hikers Missing for Three Days Are Found Alive
headline.print_headline: Montana: Two Hikers Missing For Three Days Are Found Alive
